Package: supplynet
Type: Package
Title: Supply network design and robustness assessment tools
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Milo Monnier
Maintainer: Milo Monnier <milo.monnier@inrae.fr>
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Milo Monnier <milo.monnier@inrae.fr> [aut, cre]", 
    "Maxime Lenormand <maxime.lenormand@inrae.fr> [ctb]",
    "Dino Ienco <dino.enco@inrae.fr> [ctb]"
  ))
Description: An extension of igraph package to supply networks. Supply networks
    are Directed Acyclic Graphs (DAG) composed of sources ands sinks, the 
    starts and the ends of supply chains. Includes function to assess diverse 
    robustness and efficiency metrics of supply networks. Implements an
    extension to spatial dimension with sf package.
